Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.29,0:06:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我对纱雾有所亏欠，我也明白我说过要公正不阿\N\N{\fs27\b0}I owe a lot to sagiri and I know I said I would stay unbiased
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.37,0:06:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,但「埃罗芒阿老师」最终是第一个使我受欢迎的模因\N\N{\fs27\b0}but in the end 「Eromanga Sensei」 was one of my first big memes that got me quite popular
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.08,0:06:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,而纱雾是那其中的核心\N\N{\fs27\b0}and sagari was right in the middle of that
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.52,0:06:37.43,Default,,0,0,0,,所以FBI模因在上\N\N{\fs27\b0}so FBI Memes aside
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.43,0:06:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,出于我个人[情感]\N\N{\fs27\b0}on a personal level
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.61,0:06:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,这儿她只能有唯一的归宿\N\N{\fs27\b0}there's only one place i could really put her
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.62,0:06:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,,凉宫春日「凉宫春日的忧郁」\N\N{\fs27\b0}「Haruhi Suzumiya」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.85,0:06:50.49,Default,,0,0,0,,想象一下这种渴求朋友[的状态]以至于大家围在你身边的唯一理由是要阻止TMD世界末日\N\N{\fs27\b0}imagine being so desperate for friends that the only reason anyone hangs out you is to prevent the fucking apocalypse
