Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.14,0:06:54.19,Default,,0,0,0,,这是你能在动画里找到最接近中毒瘾的东西\N\N{\fs27\b0}this is the closest thing in anime you'd find to a drug addiction
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.19,0:06:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你过的不顺心\N\N{\fs27\b0}if you're having bad day
