Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.37,0:07:15.49,Default,,0,0,0,,远坂凛「Fate Stay night」\N\N{\fs27\b0}「Rin Tousaka」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.49,0:07:17.14,Default,,0,0,0,,凛永远在最佳老婆里占有一席之地\N\N{\fs27\b0}Rin will always be one of the greatest
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.14,0:07:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,因为对我来说\N\N{\fs27\b0}because to me
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.06,0:07:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,凛有着蹭得累的最高品质\N\N{\fs27\b0}Rin involves the highest quality at tsundere can be
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.84,0:07:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,而且一直是一个单纯的傲娇\N\N{\fs27\b0}while still being a pure tsundere
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.26,0:07:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,这些最佳老婆们有些混着傲娇特质或不时有傲娇时刻\N\N{\fs27\b0}some of this top tier girls have tsun traits and tsun moment that are blended with other things
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.82,0:07:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,但是凛并非一个成功将自己和其他角色区分开来的傲娇\N\N{\fs27\b0}but Rin isn't out-and-out tsundere that manages to differentiate herself from the rest
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.26,0:07:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,她是每个傲娇特质都被提纯到最高品质的产物\N\N{\fs27\b0}she is what happens when every tsundere traits refined to the highest degree
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.64,0:07:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,双马尾\N\N{\fs27\b0}she has the twin tails
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.80,0:07:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,,长筒袜\N\N{\fs27\b0}she has the thigh-highs
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.91,0:07:42.69,Default,,0,0,0,,值得让我能立刻去世重生到异世界守护的害羞腮红\N\N{\fs27\b0}she has the blush I'd literally die in reincarnate into another world to protect
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.69,0:07:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,以及一个傲娇的完美平衡\N\N{\fs27\b0}and the mix between tsun and dere a so perfectly balanced
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.10,0:07:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,她一个人就能成为对应灭霸响指攻击的终极武器\N\N{\fs27\b0}she alone could have been the most effective weapon against Thanos snap
