Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.38,0:07:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,宫园薰「四月是你的谎言」剧透警告\N\N{\fs27\b0}「Caori」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.95,0:08:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你看过一个动画角色竟能花两季去十指相拥或是五年去坦白嘛\N\N{\fs27\b0}you know how an anime characters will stereotypically wait for like two seasons before holding hand and like five years to confess
