Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.61,0:08:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,史比特瓦根包含了一个老婆需要的所有品质，甚至还有富余\N\N{\fs27\b0}SpeedWagon embodies everything a waifu should be and more
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.26,0:08:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道你们在想些什么\N\N{\fs27\b0} but I know what you're thinking
