Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.58,0:08:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,你们太短视拉\N\N{\fs27\b0}and that's so short-sighted
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.25,0:08:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,因为你们没有注意到老婆是靠心的\N\N{\fs27\b0}because you fail to see that waifu wisdom is in the heart
