Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.52,0:08:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,他不是基佬\N\N{\fs27\b0}he isn't gay
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.84,0:08:46.26,Default,,0,0,0,,他只是找不到指的托付的女士了\N\N{\fs27\b0}he simply ran out of women that were worthy
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.26,0:08:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,你喜欢史比特瓦根\N\N{\fs27\b0}you like SpeedWagon
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.98,0:08:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,有哪个男的能拒绝他的魅力呢\N\N{\fs27\b0}what kind of man doesn't
